<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer41785704818047360">Marcus Tullius Cicero, Roman philosopher, statesman, lawyer, political theorist, and Roman constitutionalist. Cicero is widely considered one of Rome&apos;s greatest orators and prose stylists.<br/><br/>Alternate profiles:<br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/16835308.Marco_Tulio_Cicer_n' title='Marco Tulio Cicerón' rel='nofollow noopener'>Marco Tulio Cicerón</a><br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/16962536.Cic_ron' title='Cicéron' rel='nofollow noopener'>Cicéron</a><br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/15605873.Cicer_n' title='Cicerón' rel='nofollow noopener'>Cicerón</a><br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/19252680.Ciceron' title='Ciceron' rel='nofollow noopener'>Ciceron</a><br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/19111811.Cicero' title='Cicero' rel='nofollow noopener'>Cicero</a><br/><br/>Note: All editions should have Marcus Tullius Cicero as primary author. Editions with another name on the cover should have that name added as seco</span>
  <span id="freeText41785704818047360" style="display:none">Marcus Tullius Cicero, Roman philosopher, statesman, lawyer, political theorist, and Roman constitutionalist. Cicero is widely considered one of Rome's greatest orators and prose stylists.<br /><br />Alternate profiles:<br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/16835308.Marco_Tulio_Cicer_n" title="Marco Tulio Cicerón" rel="nofollow noopener">Marco Tulio Cicerón</a><br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/16962536.Cic_ron" title="Cicéron" rel="nofollow noopener">Cicéron</a><br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/15605873.Cicer_n" title="Cicerón" rel="nofollow noopener">Cicerón</a><br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/19252680.Ciceron" title="Ciceron" rel="nofollow noopener">Ciceron</a><br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/19111811.Cicero" title="Cicero" rel="nofollow noopener">Cicero</a><br /><br />Note: All editions should have Marcus Tullius Cicero as primary author. Editions with another name on the cover should have that name added as secondary author.<br /><br /></span>
